column3: “Black Domina is a phenomenal strain, and this offspring is an exceptional one. Jack Herer mother gives you a more energized version of it's partner, while Black Domina can be very sedating it prevents this strain from being a total knock out. You float in-between the best of both worlds with one being indica & the other sativa. It's an even hybrid to me, can consume anytime of day.”
“This strain is ok but its not that strong at all.”
“Smells like iced sweet tea, tastes like sweet candy flowers. Yes please.”
